@section Image files
When you open an image file with the `.png`, `.gif`, `.jpg`, `.jpeg` or `.bmp` extension then an import wizard can be
started to convert the color image to a black and white image.


The way images are handled can be configured from the `Editor` tab in the `Settings dialog`.
This dialog can be found in the `File` menu. You can select if the image type should be opened with
the import dialog, should be viewed or if you should be prompted with a dialog on how to handle the loading.
+------------------------------+-----------+--------------------------------------------+
| Icon                         | Extension | Description                                |
+------------------------------+-----------+--------------------------------------------+
| @image images/files/rgf.svg  | rgf       | Robot graphic file, momochrome image file. |
| @image images/files/png.svg  | png       | Image file, can be converted or viewed.    |
| @image images/files/gif.svg  | gif       | Image file, can be converted or viewed.    |
| @image images/files/jpg.svg  | jpg/jpeg  | Image file, can be converted or viewed.    |
| @image images/files/bmp.svg  | bmp       | Image file, can be converted or viewed.    |
| @image images/files/svg.svg  | svg       | Image file, can be viewed.                 |
+------------------------------+-----------+--------------------------------------------+

@section Sound files
When you open a sound file with the `.mp3`, `.wav` or `.ogg` extension then an import wizard will be
started to convert the sound file to a 8kHz file. Unfortunately the conversion leads to a large loss of sound quality.
+------------------------------+-----------+--------------------------------------------+
| Icon                         | Extension | Description                                |
+------------------------------+-----------+--------------------------------------------+
| @image images/files/rsf.svg  | rsf       | Robot sound file, 8kHz sound sample.       |
| @image images/files/mp3.svg  | mp3       | Sound file.                                |
| @image images/files/wav.svg  | wav       | Sound file.                                |
| @image images/files/ogg.svg  | ogg       | Sound file.                                |
+------------------------------+-----------+--------------------------------------------+

